"title": "6746: sanctification, means and results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6746: sanctification, means and results of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sanctification results from the renewing work of the Holy Spirit and leads to the renewal of believers and their being equipped for ministry in the world.</p>\n<h2>The means of sanctification</h2>\n<h3>The work of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9-Rom8:11\">ROM 8:9–8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:15-Rom15:16\">ROM 15:15–15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:4–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1-1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Meditation on the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2-1Pet2:3\">1PE 2:2–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:18\">DEU 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:12-Ps119:18\">PSA 119:12–119:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:48\">PSA 119:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5-Ps143:6\">PSA 143:5–143:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17\">JHN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">JAS 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>The active pursuit of holiness and righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11-1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:11–6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:22\">1TH 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:9–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:11\">3JN 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience and self-denial</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19-Rom6:22\">ROM 6:19–6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:14\">ROM 8:5–8:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:24\">GAL 5:16–5:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:18\">PSA 145:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:8\">MAT 7:7–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20\">JUD 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Confession of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:6-Neh1:9\">NEH 1:6–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:5\">PSA 32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:11-Ps40:12\">PSA 40:11–40:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:13\">PRO 28:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:5-Isa64:7\">ISA 64:5–64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:20-Jer14:22\">JER 14:20–14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:40\">LAM 3:40</a></p>\n<h2>Obstacles to sanctification</h2>\n<h3>A lack of faith</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13\">MAT 5:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">JHN 15:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20-2Cor12:21\">2CO 12:20–12:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:18-1Tim1:19\">1TI 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:24\">EZK 18:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15-Deut32:18\">DEU 32:15–32:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:26\">JOB 34:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:11-Isa65:12\">ISA 65:11–65:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:7\">GAL 1:6–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:7-Gal5:9\">GAL 5:7–5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:15\">HEB 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:4-Rev2:5\">REV 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Satanic temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8-1Pet5:9\">1PE 5:8–5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:8-2Cor2:11\">2CO 2:8–2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Self-indulgence and greed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:21\">2CO 12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:19\">EPH 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Yielding to sinful desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14\">1PE 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:18-Mark4:19\">MRK 4:18–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:6-1Cor10:8\">1CO 10:6–10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:14-2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:14–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16-1John2:17\">1JN 2:16–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>The results of sanctification</h2>\n<h3>Good works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:8\">2CO 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15-Col3:17\">COL 3:15–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24-Heb10:25\">HEB 10:24–10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:26\">JAS 2:14–2:26</a></p>\n<h3>Becoming like Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:27\">GAL 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Becoming like God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:21-Col1:22\">COL 1:21–1:22</a></p>\n<h3>Perfection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a></p>\n<h3>Blamelessness in the sight of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:14\">2PE 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:21-Col1:22\">COL 1:21–1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">1TH 5:23</a></p>\n<h3>Being able to see God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a></p>",
